ying =E2=80=9Cskimp on the =0Ameat but don=E2=80=99t tell anyone!=E2=80=9D =
=E2=80=94 but you can=E2=80=99t prove it forevery burrito for every=0Acusto=
mer. Maybe you can get a few customers to testify tearfully about how =0Atr=
aumatized they were by not having enough meat in their burritos, but you =
=0Acan=E2=80=99t practically getmillions of customers to do that, and the o=
