n=E2=80=99t know, I am tired and embarrassed just typing this. But the othe=
r, more =0Aconvenient victims here are Chipotle=E2=80=99s shareholders. Her=
e=E2=80=99sthe actual complaint =0Ain this case =0A<https://assets.bwbx.io/=
documents/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ruqvkTjfu6Uk/v0>; it=E2=80=99s 20 =0Apages and=
